column1:
ما أسرف أحد في المحبة إلا وانقلبت محبته عداوة ولو بعد حين،
والرفق والاعتدال حسن في كل شيء، وخير الرفق ما كان في المحبة،
فترفق بنفسك وبمن تحب، 
وأحبب هونا ما، وأبغض هونا ما، 
واعلم أنك مهما أقمت فإنك مفارق عن قريب

Copied

Life is not just about photos, I decided to follow the idea of a friend, in a game called "meeting between friends". the idea is to see who reads a post without pictures. If no one reads my wall, it will be a short experience, but if you read this message, please write a word about both of us. Just a word. For example, a place that makes you think of me, an object, a moment, a restaurant, a coffee, a sport, a movie... and then copy this message on your wall and I'll leave Please don't leave the word if you don't have time to copy the text. It would ruin the pleasure of the game.
